<h3 id="what-do-we-expect-from-budget">What do we expect from Budget?</h3>

<hr />

<p><img src="/images/budgeting-tool/budget-sheets.png" alt="Budget Sheets" /></p>

<p>The proposed budgeting tool will incorporate two distinct sheets: a â€˜Budgetâ€™ sheet for resource allocation and a â€˜Transactionsâ€™ sheet for recording financial transactions. The â€˜Budgetâ€™ sheet is intended to be established at the commencement of each month, with subsequent modifications primarily occurring within the â€˜Transactionsâ€™ sheet. It is anticipated that updates to the â€˜Transactionsâ€™ sheet will automatically reflect in the â€˜Budgetâ€™ sheet, ensuring real-time accuracy of the budgeting data.</p>

<h3 id="doing-this-in-numbers"><strong>Doing this in Numbers</strong></h3>

<hr />

<p>Fortunately, all these functionalities are incorporated within a pre-constructed default template in Numbers, providing a seamless user experience.</p>

